This project is inspired by Walter Bislin's Advanced Earth Curvature
Calculator:

https://walter.bislins.ch/bloge/index.asp?page=Advanced+Earth+Curvature+Calculator

Walter Bislin's original calculator and published source-code pages are used
as reference material for understanding the feature set, equations, controls,
and visualization behavior that GeoSight aims to study and reimplement in a
modern TypeScript application.

The repository includes a jsgx3d folder for reference while developing the
visualization. In particular, jsgx3d/src/x.js contains its own notice:

